  "content_html": "<p>काठमाडौँ – बुधबार पर्ने विश्वकर्मा पूजाका लागि माटोका मूर्ति बनाउने र बेच्ने काम तीव्र रूपमा भइरहेको छ।</p>\n<p>शिल्पीहरूले मूर्तिहरू तयार पार्दै बजारमा बिक्रीका लागि ल्याएका छन्। पूजाको दिन भक्तजनहरूले पूजा र औजारको आराधना गर्छन्।</p>\n<p>विश्वकर्मा पूजा, हिन्दू परम्परामा देवताका वास्तुकार विश्वकर्मालाई समर्पित पर्व हो, जसमा औजार, कार्यस्थल र मेशिनहरूको पूजा गरेर समृद्धि, सुरक्षा र दक्षता प्राप्त हुने विश्वास गरिन्छ।</p>\n<p>यस पर्वले व्यक्तिहरू र समुदायहरूलाई औजार, मेशिन र दक्ष शिल्पीहरूको महत्व स्मरण गराउने अवसर पनि प्रदान गर्दछ। पूजा सकिएपछि भक्तजनहरूले मूर्तिहरू विभिन्न खोलामा विसर्जन गर्छन्।</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094563\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16183002/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-11-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094564\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16183003/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-12-1024x682.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094565\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16183003/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-13-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094566\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16183004/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-14-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094561\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182947/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-9-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094560\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182947/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-8-1024x682.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094559\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182946/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-7-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094558\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182946/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-6-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094557\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182931/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-5-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094556\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182931/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-4-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094555\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182930/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-3-1024x682.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094554\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182930/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-2-1024x683.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /> <img alt=\"\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-1094553\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://assets.deshsanchar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/16182929/Bishwakarma-Murti_Nepal-Photo-Library-1-1024x682.jpeg\" width=\"1024\" /></p>\n<p>तस्बिरहरू: सफल प्रकाश श्रेष्ठ/नेपाल फोटो लाइब्रेरी</p>",
